193
00:17:17,625 --> 00:17:19,125
陈科
Chief Chen,

194
00:17:19,667 --> 00:17:21,125
帮帮他吧
please help him.

195
00:17:21,125 --> 00:17:25,208
咦？这个花瓶是贵价货！
This vase must be expensive!

196
00:17:25,708 --> 00:17:27,417
小小意思
Just a modest gift.

197
00:17:27,667 --> 00:17:29,000
老规矩
Here's how it works:

198
00:17:29,000 --> 00:17:32,583
陈科玩腻了，就让回给张总！
when Chief Chen grows tired of it, Boss Zhang can buy it back!

199
00:17:32,583 --> 00:17:35,333
那至少值三十万！
It's worth at least RMB¥300K!

200
00:17:37,250 --> 00:17:39,208
不是说好了二十万吗？
Didn't we agree on RMB¥200K?

201
00:17:40,125 --> 00:17:41,708
我看错？
I got the price wrong?

202
00:17:42,375 --> 00:17:44,458
老猫烧须？
Oh, even Homer sometimes nods.

203
00:17:44,458 --> 00:17:45,667
怎会？
No way!

204
00:17:45,667 --> 00:17:48,917
说到古董，陈科才是专家
Chief Chen is a connoisseur.

205
00:17:48,917 --> 00:17:50,708
我们哪会懂，对吧？
What do we know?

206
00:17:50,708 --> 00:17:53,125
陈科说三十便三十
If Chief Chen says RMB¥300K, then it's RMB¥300K.

207
00:17:54,250 --> 00:17:56,167
明天上来工商局拿批文
Come get the business license tomorrow.

208
00:17:56,167 --> 00:17:59,500
我找个漂亮的框镶好给你
I'll have it nicely framed for you.

209
00:17:59,500 --> 00:18:00,750
谢谢陈科
Thanks so much, Chief Chen.

210
00:18:00,750 --> 00:18:02,500
好兄弟
We're buddies.

211
00:18:02,500 --> 00:18:05,250
张总，看看想吃什么？
Boss Zhang, what would you like to eat?

212
00:18:06,208 --> 00:18:08,292
咸菜扣肉
Braised pork with preserved vegetables.

213
00:18:09,292 --> 00:18:11,500
我才不吃肥腻的
That's too oily for me.

214
00:18:13,833 --> 00:18:15,042
让我来点菜
Let me order.

215
00:18:15,292 --> 00:18:18,042
就吃鱼虾蟹海鲜餐，好吗？
Shall we have a seafood platter?

216
00:18:18,458 --> 00:18:19,875
我去叫
Let me order it.

217
00:18:19,875 --> 00:18:21,167
服务员！
Waiter!

218
00:18:21,167 --> 00:18:23,167
张总，祝你生意兴隆
Mr Zhang, best of luck with your business!

219
00:18:23,167 --> 00:18:24,708
好，多谢
Thanks a lot.

220
00:18:25,292 --> 00:18:26,167
喝一杯
Cheers.

221
00:18:26,167 --> 00:18:26,833
干
Bottoms up!

222
00:18:27,208 --> 00:18:28,542
干！
Bottoms up!

223
00:18:38,375 --> 00:18:42,208
这一个，逢星期日，打高球，清水湾
This guy plays golf every Sunday in Clear Water Bay.

224
00:18:42,208 --> 00:18:47,500
单行路，够清静，电话有盲点，可以考虑
One-way road. Quiet. No phone signal. It may work.

225
00:18:47,500 --> 00:18:49,292
饭还没到吗？
Hey! Where's our rice?

226
00:18:49,292 --> 00:18:50,500
下一个
Next.

227
00:18:51,333 --> 00:18:53,125
这个好办
This one is easy.

228
00:18:53,125 --> 00:18:55,250
超级玩家
A super playboy.

229
00:18:55,250 --> 00:18:57,667
每晚喝到天昏地暗
Drunk every night.

230
00:18:58,958 --> 00:19:01,708
最近还包养了小明星
He recently has an actress as a mistress.

231
00:19:04,708 --> 00:19:05,625
喂
Hey!

232
00:19:05,625 --> 00:19:06,542
饭呢？
Where is our rice?

233
00:19:06,542 --> 00:19:07,917
饭，稍等我一下
Rice? Give me a second.

234
00:19:07,917 --> 00:19:09,625
饭马上来，很快
Your rice is coming right away.

235
00:19:11,083 --> 00:19:13,000
有时候，司机会被支开
Sometimes he would send his driver away.

236
00:19:13,000 --> 00:19:15,125
不好意思，让你们久等
Sorry to keep you waiting.

237
00:19:15,125 --> 00:19:16,333
请慢用
Enjoy your food.

238
00:19:16,750 --> 00:19:18,000
关门
Close the door.

239
00:19:21,625 --> 00:19:23,542
先生，这边请
Sir, please follow me.

240
00:19:23,792 --> 00:19:25,042
给我一杯茶
Give me a cup of tea.

241
00:19:25,042 --> 00:19:26,542
喂！你刚不是去厕所吗？
Hey! Haven't you gone to the bathroom just now?

242
00:19:26,542 --> 00:19:28,375
不要吐　　饭是冷的！
- Wait! Don't puke.    - Hey! The rice is cold!

243
00:19:28,375 --> 00:19:29,458
你稍等我一下
Give me a second.

244
00:19:29,458 --> 00:19:30,958
不好意思，饭是冷的吗？　　我要茶！
- I'm sorry. The rice is cold?    - I want tea.

245
00:19:30,958 --> 00:19:32,458
快点　　小姐，麻烦你告诉我⋯
- Hurry up!    - Tell me the room number…

246
00:19:32,458 --> 00:19:34,625
我要茶！　　等我一下，我带你去
- I want tea.    - Give me a second. I'll show you the way.

247
00:19:34,625 --> 00:19:35,542
茶，我帮你拿
Sure, I'll get you tea.

248
00:19:35,542 --> 00:19:38,042
等一下，你们都等我一下，马上回来
Give me a second. I will be right back.

249
00:19:40,667 --> 00:19:42,625
将就一下吧
Take it easy.

250
00:19:42,625 --> 00:19:45,333
上来聊才能甩掉那些狗仔队
We came to China to shake off those cop dogs.

251
00:19:45,333 --> 00:19:46,458
你上次玩得那么大！
You went too far last time!

252
00:19:46,458 --> 00:19:48,750
要玩就玩大的
I live life to the full.

253
00:19:49,833 --> 00:19:51,958
人生就这样
C'est la vie.

254
00:19:51,958 --> 00:19:53,583
不然怎么精彩？
There's no other way.

255
00:19:57,250 --> 00:20:01,875
我们之前偷车、爆窃、打劫运钞车
We've stolen cars, committed burglaries,

256
00:20:01,875 --> 00:20:03,250
一次比一次厉害！
and robbed cash vans.

257
00:20:04,250 --> 00:20:07,125
连大富翁都动了
We even kidnapped the tycoon's son.

258
00:20:07,125 --> 00:20:08,625
还绑架？
Should we do more kidnappings?

259
00:20:10,583 --> 00:20:12,333
那你想到什么好主意？
What do you have in mind?

260
00:20:13,250 --> 00:20:15,292
说出来，我们商量一下
Spit it out. We can discuss.

261
00:20:38,875 --> 00:20:41,208
我是一个攀山运动员
I'm a mountaineer.

262
00:20:41,875 --> 00:20:43,583
我征服了一座山
After conquering one mountain,

263
00:20:43,583 --> 00:20:47,208
当然得再找一座更高、更难爬的山
I need to find a higher and harder mountain.

264
00:20:48,125 --> 00:20:49,708
就这样
That's it.

265
00:20:52,417 --> 00:20:54,000
还没找到那座山
Before finding that mountain,

266
00:20:54,000 --> 00:20:55,875
先找钱吧
let's find the money first.

267
00:20:57,583 --> 00:20:58,792
继续
Let's keep doing it.

268
00:21:00,000 --> 00:21:02,375
郑建权，五十三岁
Cheng, 53 years old.

269
00:21:02,375 --> 00:21:05,792
没儿没女，老婆当家
No children. His wife is in charge.

270
00:21:06,542 --> 00:21:10,125
以前一万多块钱一部，谁买得起？
A mobile phone used to cost over RMB¥10K. Who could afford that?

271
00:21:10,125 --> 00:21:12,792
你以为谁都是高干子弟？
Not everyone is a child of a high-ranking official.

272
00:21:14,375 --> 00:21:16,500
现在愈便宜愈好
Now the cheaper, the better.

273
00:21:17,833 --> 00:21:20,250
我们一千万人口
We have a population of 10 million.

274
00:21:20,250 --> 00:21:22,708
你算算
Say RMB¥1K a set,

275
00:21:24,625 --> 00:21:27,208
对，一千块钱一部
RMB¥10K for 10 sets.

276
00:21:27,208 --> 00:21:30,833
十部就一万块，那时候就发过周润发了
We will be fatter than Chow Yun-fat!

277
00:21:31,917 --> 00:21:35,708
对，现在没人用传呼机了
Beepers are already outdated.

278
00:21:36,958 --> 00:21:41,542
好了，不说了，谈正事，一会儿再聊
OK, I'll talk to you later.

279
00:21:44,667 --> 00:21:47,125
潮哥，不好意思
Excuse me, Boss.

280
00:21:50,917 --> 00:21:52,333
继续讲吧
Please go on.

281
00:21:53,250 --> 00:21:56,750
你别难为小的了，小生意
Don't give us a hard time. We're doing small business.

282
00:21:56,750 --> 00:22:01,833
不说我的事了，潮哥，这帮小弟很棒
Big Bro, these kids are great.

283
00:22:02,583 --> 00:22:04,542
走最前的老鬼在香港有案底
The guy who came in first has criminal record in Hong Kong.

284
00:22:04,542 --> 00:22:06,208
你带来有个屁用
Don't know why you brought him here.

285
00:22:06,917 --> 00:22:08,750
混蛋，叫你带些像样的来
I told you to bring some decent-looking guys.

286
00:22:08,750 --> 00:22:11,458
