They all look like criminals and idiots.

287
00:22:12,000 --> 00:22:15,375
干你娘的，你该收山了
You should be out of business.

288
00:22:20,542 --> 00:22:22,083
他看什么？
What is he staring at?

289
00:22:25,917 --> 00:22:29,417
