I don't want the guy in blue either.

291
00:22:35,125 --> 00:22:37,000
这次两个就够了？
You only need two men this time?

292
00:22:37,917 --> 00:22:40,792
带他们去开开眼界嘛
Take the others to broaden their horizons.

293
00:22:46,500 --> 00:22:49,250
明白，完全明白
Got it!

294
00:22:49,250 --> 00:22:50,917
我去安排
Let me see to it.

295
00:22:52,750 --> 00:22:55,833
你看看看，他妈的看什么？
What are you fucking looking at?

296
00:22:55,833 --> 00:22:58,375
走了，向阳、老胡
You, you, get lost!

297
00:22:58,375 --> 00:23:01,708
走了！别喝了！走了！
Stop drinking and scram!

298
00:23:01,708 --> 00:23:03,958
你们两个，跟我进来
You two come with me.

299
00:23:08,000 --> 00:23:09,833
快点了，快点了
Faster.

300
00:23:09,833 --> 00:23:11,417
慢死了
So slow!

301
00:23:14,208 --> 00:23:15,542
潮哥
Big Bro Chiu,

302
00:23:15,542 --> 00:23:16,667
王磊
Wang Lei.

303
00:23:16,667 --> 00:23:17,958
红旗
Hong Qi.

304
00:23:17,958 --> 00:23:19,000
叫潮哥
Say Big Bro Chiu.

305
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:19,917
潮哥！
Big Bro Chiu!

306
00:23:21,375 --> 00:23:22,333
听得懂广东话吧？
They understand Cantonese?

307
00:23:22,333 --> 00:23:25,208
懂，当然懂
Of course!

308
00:23:26,417 --> 00:23:29,333
来！先喝一杯
Come have a drink.

309
00:23:29,667 --> 00:23:31,125
装扮一下来香港见我
Spruce them up before sending them to Hong Kong.

310
00:23:31,125 --> 00:23:33,583
好，一定，我会的
Sure will!

311
00:23:48,125 --> 00:23:49,417
他妈的
Motherfucker.

312
00:23:49,417 --> 00:23:51,042
坐，吃饭
Sit and eat.

313
00:23:54,833 --> 00:23:56,083
连长
Commander,

314
00:23:56,083 --> 00:23:57,875
这潮哥是什么来头？
who's this Big Bro Chiu?

315
00:23:59,208 --> 00:24:02,167
他就是不让你知道他什么来头
Who cares if he is Big Bro Chiu or not?

316
00:24:05,958 --> 00:24:07,500
他这个贱人
He is a douchebag.

317
