就换一个名字的老狐狸
old fox who changes identities.

319
00:24:12,792 --> 00:24:16,500
跟他妈早年香港那个隐形贼王季正雄
He looks fucking like Kwai Ching-hung,

320
00:24:16,500 --> 00:24:18,292
一个他妈的样子
the invisible King of Thieves in Hong Kong.

321
00:24:19,125 --> 00:24:21,958
那个季正雄杀掉警察被通缉
Kwai Ching-hung disappeared

322
00:24:21,958 --> 00:24:23,542
就销声匿迹了
after killing cops.

323
00:24:23,625 --> 00:24:26,417
然后又蹦出个潮哥出来
Then Big Bro Chiu popped up.

324
00:24:26,417 --> 00:24:30,333
「潮哥」，不就是个名字而已
Big Bro Chiu is just a name.

325
00:24:51,917 --> 00:24:53,458
大辉在吗？
Is Fai here?

326
00:24:54,250 --> 00:24:55,792
阿辉
Fai.

327
00:24:56,667 --> 00:24:57,417
什么事？
What's up?

328
00:24:57,417 --> 00:24:59,083
有人找你　　喂
- Someone is looking for you.    - Hey.

329
00:25:01,333 --> 00:25:02,625
可乐哥
Bro Coke?

330
00:25:03,333 --> 00:25:04,167
喂
Hey!

331
00:25:04,167 --> 00:25:04,917
泰国人？
She's Thai?

332
00:25:04,917 --> 00:25:06,375
Noon，去买可乐
Noon, go buy a dozen of Cokes.

333
00:25:06,375 --> 00:25:07,583
你什么时候回来的？
When did you come back?

334
00:25:07,583 --> 00:25:08,792
刚刚回来
Just now.

335
00:25:09,542 --> 00:25:12,125
你干什么？这么客气，进来坐
You are too kind. Come in and have a seat.

336
00:25:12,125 --> 00:25:13,125
你说泰语吗？
Did you just speak Thai?

337
00:25:13,125 --> 00:25:15,250
难道我讲法语吗？
Do you think I speak French?

338
00:25:33,000 --> 00:25:34,208
好臭！
You stink!

339
