宝儿
Bo.

341
00:25:37,000 --> 00:25:38,750
你怎能这么没规矩？
How can you be so rude?

342
00:25:38,750 --> 00:25:40,542
进去帮爸爸开饭
Come help set the table.

343
00:25:41,083 --> 00:25:42,625
你坐一下，很快开饭
Dinner will be served soon.

344
00:25:43,417 --> 00:25:44,708
你真顽皮
Naughty girl.

345
00:25:45,000 --> 00:25:45,833
去洗手
Go wash your hands.

346
00:25:45,833 --> 00:25:47,333
刚才洗过了
I did wash my hands.

347
00:25:48,083 --> 00:25:51,333
你昨天吃过饭，今天要不要吃？就是嘛
You ate yesterday. Are you going to eat today?

348
00:25:52,917 --> 00:25:55,708
慢慢来，宝儿，这么着急
Bo, slow down. Don't rush.

349
00:25:55,708 --> 00:25:57,125
可乐哥
Bro Coke.

350
00:25:59,417 --> 00:26:00,417
想喝吗？
You want some?

351
00:26:00,417 --> 00:26:02,208
我跟你一人一半吧
Shall we share it?

352
00:26:03,917 --> 00:26:04,875
别让她喝
Don't let her drink it.

353
00:26:04,875 --> 00:26:07,292
早前又咳嗽了，不然又要花钱看医生
She was coughing. I don't wanna spend money on meds.

354
00:26:07,292 --> 00:26:09,250
我没咳嗽，只是发烧而已
I wasn't coughing. I just had a fever.

355
00:26:09,250 --> 00:26:11,000
对，只是喝一点
It's all right to have a sip.

356
00:26:11,000 --> 00:26:13,042
什么没咳嗽？你就会顶嘴！
Not coughing? You are being cheeky!

357
00:26:13,042 --> 00:26:14,417
总之不能喝
I say no Coke.

358
00:26:21,792 --> 00:26:24,792
辉，我不吃，快要迟到
Fai, I'm not gonna eat. I'm running late.

359
00:26:26,042 --> 00:26:27,125
现在就出去？
You're going now?

360
00:26:27,125 --> 00:26:27,875
是的
Yes.

361
00:26:31,708 --> 00:26:33,667
乖乖的
Be a good girl.

362
00:26:36,750 --> 00:26:38,333
可乐哥，吃饭
Bro Coke, dig in.

363
00:26:39,167 --> 00:26:40,250
她不吃？
She's not eating with us?

364
00:26:40,250 --> 00:26:42,167
她去上夜班
She has to work night shift.

365
00:26:45,250 --> 00:26:47,167
她做按摩师的
She's a legit masseuse.

366
00:26:48,375 --> 00:26:49,917
吃块烧肉
Eat some barbecued pork.

367
00:26:50,250 --> 00:26:51,917
来，吃蔬菜
Bo, eat some veggies.

368
00:26:51,917 --> 00:26:53,542
经常不吃蔬菜
You seldom eat veggies.

369
00:26:55,875 --> 00:26:57,750
去不去海洋公园？
Shall we go to Ocean Park?

370
00:27:00,458 --> 00:27:02,208
玩过云霄飞车吗？想玩吗？
Shall we ride the roller coaster?

371
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:10,083
我带你飞高一点，远一点，好吗？
Shall we fly higher and farther?

372
00:27:10,083 --> 00:27:14,125
不答我？搔你痒
Tickle, tickle.

373
00:27:18,625 --> 00:27:20,583
不要那么吵，要不然房东太太又骂人了
Stop making noise, or the landlady will be nasty.

374
00:27:20,583 --> 00:27:22,833
她骂你没交房租吧
She's nasty because you haven't paid the rent.

375
00:27:22,833 --> 00:27:24,333
还顶嘴，下来
You're being cheeky. Come down.

376
00:27:24,333 --> 00:27:27,000
厉害，臭丫头，敢跟老爸顶嘴
What a dragon lady, arguing with your father!

377
00:27:27,417 --> 00:27:30,375
这丫头，一玩就忘形了！穿好拖鞋
This girl plays too much! Wear your slippers.

378
00:27:30,375 --> 00:27:33,458
做好功课没有？快点，进去做功课
Have you finished your homework? Homework first.

379
00:27:33,458 --> 00:27:34,542
快点！
Quick!

380
00:27:36,000 --> 00:27:37,792
我待会打你屁股　　真乖
- I'll spank you.    - Good girl.

381
00:27:38,750 --> 00:27:40,625
这丫头！
This naughty girl!

