"Whoring, gambling, drinking, roaming…

386
00:27:47,917 --> 00:27:49,583
戒了不够帅」
and smoking are the hobbies of a king."

387
00:27:49,583 --> 00:27:51,125
是你说的
Your mantra.

388
00:27:54,042 --> 00:27:56,708
我要洗肾，不戒不行
I'm on dialysis. I have to quit.

389
00:27:57,750 --> 00:27:59,000
早就说你肾亏
Told you you're impotent.

390
00:27:59,000 --> 00:28:00,083
一蹲下就头晕
You feel dizzy when you squat.

391
00:28:00,083 --> 00:28:01,125
去！
Fuck!

392
00:28:02,625 --> 00:28:04,208
最近在干什么？
What have you been up to?

393
00:28:04,542 --> 00:28:06,292
我可以干什么？
What can I do?

394
00:28:06,292 --> 00:28:08,333
以前干地盘临时工
I used to do temporary construction work.

395
00:28:08,333 --> 00:28:09,625
现在全职带女儿
Now I'm a full-time babysitter.

396
00:28:09,625 --> 00:28:11,375
你呢？
What about you?

397
00:28:11,375 --> 00:28:12,375
我？
Me?

398
00:28:13,083 --> 00:28:15,208
我卖这个去大陆
I sell this in China.

399
00:28:16,542 --> 00:28:18,583
以后没有人用传呼机了
People won't use beepers anymore.

400
00:28:18,875 --> 00:28:20,708
将来大陆人一人一部
Every Chinese will own a mobile phone in the future.

401
00:28:20,708 --> 00:28:23,458
一部卖一千，十部一万
One sells for RMB¥1K, 10 for RMB¥10K.

402
00:28:23,458 --> 00:28:24,792
发过周润发
I'll be fatter than Chow Yun-fat.

403
00:28:24,792 --> 00:28:26,458
那么发？
Fat with loads of money?

404
00:28:26,958 --> 00:28:29,250
真厉害
Great.

405
00:28:32,167 --> 00:28:35,167
你真好，做老板了
You're doing great. You're becoming a boss.

406
00:28:36,750 --> 00:28:41,667
也对，走正路总比以前走偏门好
Going straight is better than going astray.

407
00:28:41,667 --> 00:28:44,583
我和你都不够狠，做不成大贼
We're not fierce enough to be Kings of Thieves.

408
00:28:44,583 --> 00:28:47,292
尽干些偷鸡摸狗的勾当
All we did were some petty crimes.

409
00:28:47,292 --> 00:28:51,500
生活没保障，觉也睡不好
Our life was insecure. We couldn't sleep well.

410
00:28:51,500 --> 00:28:54,958
又不是赚很多，也不知为了什么
And we didn't earn that much. So what's the point?

411
00:29:01,250 --> 00:29:03,083
我想在这里住几天
I'd like to stay here for a few days.

412
00:29:03,083 --> 00:29:03,833
什么？
What?

413
00:29:03,833 --> 00:29:05,292
我睡沙发就可以
I can sleep on the couch.

414
00:29:06,625 --> 00:29:07,500
干什么？
What's that for?

415
00:29:07,500 --> 00:29:11,333
收下吧，帮补一下阿嫂
Take it. It will lessen your wife's burden.

416
00:29:12,750 --> 00:29:16,208
爸爸，手册不见了！
Dad, I can't find my school manual!

417
00:29:16,833 --> 00:29:18,292
爸爸，爸爸
Dad, Dad.

418
00:29:18,292 --> 00:29:19,583
来了！
Coming!

419
00:29:21,542 --> 00:29:22,667
行了
That's fine

420
00:29:38,083 --> 00:29:40,625
(Gold shop)

421
00:29:51,125 --> 00:29:54,333
(Jockey Club)

422
00:29:54,333 --> 00:29:57,083
番禺易发市场
Panyu Yi Fa Market

423
00:29:59,167 --> 00:30:01,667
三十部廿九吋新画皇，每部一万二
30 sets of 29-inch TVs. RMB¥12K apiece.

424
00:30:01,667 --> 00:30:04,375
另外八十部VCD机，每部四千
Plus 80 VCD players. RMB¥4K apiece.

425
00:30:04,375 --> 00:30:06,042
多谢你，六十八万
RMB¥680K, thank you.

426
00:30:09,083 --> 00:30:10,958
收了你七十万
You pay me RMB¥700K.

427
00:30:11,500 --> 00:30:12,750
货到通知你
I will notify you once the goods are delivered.

428
00:30:12,750 --> 00:30:13,958
下一个
Next.

429
00:30:13,958 --> 00:30:17,167
陈科的三十万，你点算一下
RMB¥30K for Chief Chen. Please count it.

430
00:30:19,667 --> 00:30:23,208
企业法人营业执照
Business License

431
00:30:35,167 --> 00:30:38,125
三十万，数目正确
RMB¥30K. The amount is correct.

432
00:30:39,208 --> 00:30:40,958
货到第一时间通知你
Will notify you once the goods are on board.

433
00:30:43,083 --> 00:30:45,125
替我多谢陈科
Please extend my thanks to Chief Chen.

434
00:30:46,167 --> 00:30:49,750
我家的VCD机坏了
My VCD player is broken.

435
00:30:49,750 --> 00:30:51,833
送你一部新的，金
I'll give you a new one. Kam.

436
00:30:51,833 --> 00:30:52,750
是
Yes.

437
00:30:54,333 --> 00:30:57,667
新款的三十三吋新画皇
The latest 33-inch TV set.

438
00:30:57,667 --> 00:30:59,083
好东西
Good stuff.

439
00:30:59,083 --> 00:31:00,458
也送给你吧
I'll give it to you, too.

440
00:31:00,458 --> 00:31:01,958
多谢张总
Thanks so much, Boss Zhang.

441
00:31:01,958 --> 00:31:03,000
不用客气
You're welcome.

442
00:31:04,708 --> 00:31:06,833
阿贵、阿广，拿部三十三吋新画皇
Gui, Guang, a 33-inch TV set and a VCD player.

443
00:31:06,833 --> 00:31:08,958
还有一部VCD机
Gui, Guang, a 33-inch TV set and a VCD player.

444
00:31:08,958 --> 00:31:10,292
好
Sure.

445
00:31:11,458 --> 00:31:14,167
大宝电器
Da-bao Electronics

446
00:31:15,792 --> 00:31:17,625
贪得无厌
She is greedy.

447
00:31:18,375 --> 00:31:20,167
做生意便是这样了
That's business.

448
00:31:20,417 --> 00:31:22,542
别整天摆副臭脸
Don't pull a long face all day long.

449
00:31:22,542 --> 00:31:24,208
张总！张总！
Boss Zhang, Boss Zhang.

450
00:31:24,208 --> 00:31:26,583
放心，他们俩会搞定
No worries. They will take care of it.

451
00:31:26,667 --> 00:31:28,167
快点　　什么事？
- Quick    - What's wrong?

452
00:31:28,375 --> 00:31:30,167
张总
Boss Zhang.

453
00:31:30,167 --> 00:31:31,542
什么事？
What's wrong?

454
00:31:35,042 --> 00:31:36,042
货物出事了？
Something wrong with the goods?

455
00:31:36,042 --> 00:31:38,042
不是，关门
No, close the door.

456
00:31:38,042 --> 00:31:39,667
关门
Close the door.

457
00:31:44,917 --> 00:31:49,375
嘴这么硬？打给你老婆报平安
Want to play tough guy? Call your wife now.

458
00:31:59,708 --> 00:32:01,292
打给你老婆
Call your wife now.

459
00:32:01,583 --> 00:32:02,875
报平安，混蛋
Tell your folks you're OK, asshole.

460
00:32:02,875 --> 00:32:05,000
打死我，你一分钱也拿不到
If you kill me, you won't get a cent.

461
00:32:05,000 --> 00:32:06,625
敢唬弄我？
Are you threatening me?

462
00:32:10,875 --> 00:32:12,750
卓，耐心点
Cheuk, be patient.

463
00:32:12,750 --> 00:32:15,167
他再不说，就断他粮水吧
If he doesn't talk, don't give him food or water.

464
00:32:22,292 --> 00:32:24,667
你好吵
You're so noisy.

465
00:32:25,417 --> 00:32:27,333
喂，干什么？
Hey, what are you doing?

466
00:32:27,333 --> 00:32:29,375
捡他上来，捡上来！
Get him back! Get him back!

467
00:32:29,792 --> 00:32:31,958
这里是金宝珠宝金行
This is the gold shop.

468
00:32:31,958 --> 00:32:34,042
平常会有一辆警车在门口
Usually there's a police wagon at the entrance.

469
00:32:34,042 --> 00:32:35,958
对面街有马会
Jockey Club is across the street.

470
00:32:35,958 --> 00:32:38,167
我们在里面看紧
We keep a close eye on the police wagon.

471
00:32:38,167 --> 00:32:42,083
待八时警车离去，我们立刻动手
As soon as it leaves at 8pm, we rob the gold shop right away.

472
00:32:42,583 --> 00:32:45,125
那天跑夜马，会有好多人，搞定之后⋯
It's the racing night. It will be crowded. After it's done…

473
00:32:45,125 --> 00:32:47,375
赚不了钱！　　记得要跟紧我
- There's not much money in this.    - Follow me closely.

474
00:32:48,875 --> 00:32:50,000
你刚说什么？
What did you just say?

475
00:32:52,167 --> 00:32:54,375
你们做大茶饭的
You've committed big crimes.

476
00:32:54,375 --> 00:32:57,042
怎么就打劫小金行？
Why pick this small gold shop?

477
00:32:57,042 --> 00:32:58,125
对啊
Yes,

478
00:32:58,125 --> 00:33:01,417
听人家说，你们三大贼王合作
I've heard the 3 Kings of Thieves would join forces.

479
00:33:01,625 --> 00:33:04,125
没几个亿，都有几千万了
At least millions of dollars will be involved.

480
00:33:04,917 --> 00:33:06,750
什么三大贼王？
What 3 Kings of Thieves?

481
00:33:07,500 --> 00:33:08,875
说吧！
Say it!

482
00:33:09,875 --> 00:33:13,583
欢哥，你是否真的重出江湖
Bro Foon, are you making a comeback?

483
00:33:13,583 --> 00:33:16,125
跟卓子强、季正雄
This time with Cheuk Tze-keung and Kwai Ching-hung.

484
00:33:16,125 --> 00:33:20,708
三大贼王合作做大案？
The 3 Kings of Thieves are collaborating?

485
00:33:21,625 --> 00:33:24,000
有人看到你们三人在大陆见面
Someone has seen you three meeting in China.

486
00:33:25,458 --> 00:33:27,083
你从哪儿听回来的？
Where did you hear this?

487
00:33:27,792 --> 00:33:29,375
外面全这么说
Everyone is saying that.

488
00:33:29,625 --> 00:33:31,208
这你也信！
And you believe it?

489
00:33:31,208 --> 00:33:35,167
老大不是说过，拿枪混不到饭吃！
Didn't Big Bro say you couldn't make money by toting guns?

490
00:33:35,792 --> 00:33:36,875
如果我是季正雄
If I'm Kwai,

491
00:33:36,875 --> 00:33:38,208
就不用和你们一起吃盒饭
I don't have to eat lunch boxes with you.

492
00:33:40,000 --> 00:33:41,542
蠢货
Idiots.

493
00:33:44,000 --> 00:33:45,542
神经病
That's ridiculous!

494
00:33:45,792 --> 00:33:47,458
一个「砰！砰！砰！」
Yip is all noise and fury.

495
00:33:47,458 --> 00:33:49,167
一个鬼鬼祟祟
Kwai is hush and shush.

496
00:33:49,167 --> 00:33:51,375
三个风格不一样，搞什么？
We are so different. How can it work?

497
00:33:51,542 --> 00:33:53,625
跟我走私多些电器
Smuggle more goods with me.

498
00:33:53,625 --> 00:33:55,458
一起赚到笑！
Let's make more money together!

499
00:33:56,542 --> 00:33:57,875
收到
Got it.

500
00:33:57,875 --> 00:33:59,000
英明！
Brilliant!

501
00:33:59,000 --> 00:34:03,083
有时心痒，也想重拾枪杆
Sometimes I feel like toting my gun again.

502
00:34:03,083 --> 00:34:04,750
打劫！打劫！
Robbery! Robbery!

503
00:34:04,750 --> 00:34:05,875
多威风！
That's so cool!

504
00:34:05,875 --> 00:34:07,208
你这叫威风？
You call that cool?

505
00:34:07,708 --> 00:34:09,792
老大开AK才威风！
Big Bro wielding AK-47 is cool!

506
00:34:10,583 --> 00:34:12,000
不是这样开
Not like this.

507
00:34:12,500 --> 00:34:14,042
AK后座力大
AK-47 recoil is powerful.

508
00:34:14,042 --> 00:34:15,333
不是托着
Don't hold it.

509
00:34:15,333 --> 00:34:16,458
而是按着
Press it.

510
00:34:16,458 --> 00:34:17,458
站稳马步
Stand firm.

511
00:34:17,458 --> 00:34:19,167
射他老子
Shoot the hell out of him.

512
00:34:28,917 --> 00:34:32,083
怎么了？跟就跟
What the fuck?! Join me

513
00:34:33,167 --> 00:34:35,125
不跟就回去吃屎
or go home and eat shit.

514
00:34:38,917 --> 00:34:41,500
潮哥，那⋯
Big Bro Chiu,

515
00:34:41,917 --> 00:34:45,542
我们打个小金行，能赚多少钱？
how much can we earn from robbing this gold shop?

516
00:34:52,458 --> 00:34:53,292
打不打电话？
You're calling or not?

517
00:34:53,292 --> 00:34:57,208
你们觉得，如果三大贼王合作
If the 3 Kings of Thieves join forces,

518
00:34:57,208 --> 00:34:59,042
就算开「鱼蛋档」
even if we open a fish ball stall together,

519
00:34:59,042 --> 00:35:01,417
也很轰动吧？
we will create a stir, right?

520
00:35:01,875 --> 00:35:03,875
起什么名字好呢？
What shall I call our stall?

521
00:35:03,875 --> 00:35:05,125
打不打电话？
Are you calling your family or not?

522
00:35:23,208 --> 00:35:24,875
不要睡！
Hey, wake up!

523
00:35:27,250 --> 00:35:28,458
金库？
Gold depository?

524
00:35:29,000 --> 00:35:30,250
马场？
Racecourse?

525
00:35:35,083 --> 00:35:37,083
绑架彭定康？
Kidnap Hong Kong Governor Chris Patten?

526
00:35:37,083 --> 00:35:38,958
鲁平？
The Head of Hong Kong and Macau Affairs, Lu Ping?

527
00:35:39,500 --> 00:35:40,708
不行
No way.

528
00:36:03,125 --> 00:36:04,250
搞什么？
What are you listening to?

529
00:36:04,250 --> 00:36:06,333
四大天王同台演出
The 4 Heavenly Kings singing on stage together.

530
00:36:06,333 --> 00:36:07,625
唱什么歌？
What are they singing?

531
00:36:09,458 --> 00:36:11,667
唱什么也听不到，有什么好听？
I can't hear a thing. What's so good about it?

532
00:36:12,042 --> 00:36:14,042
四大天王破天荒第一次合唱
When the 4 Heavenly Kings sing together,

533
00:36:14,042 --> 00:36:15,958
唱什么也很厉害
it's terrific no matter what they sing.

534
00:36:18,083 --> 00:36:20,792
我要水，水！
Water, give me water.

535
00:36:21,083 --> 00:36:24,000
我肯打了，我打了
I will make the call.

536
00:36:36,292 --> 00:36:38,333
我丈夫怎么样？我求求你！
How's my husband? I beg you!

537
00:36:38,333 --> 00:36:40,708
他身体不好，别为难他
He's not in good health. Don't hurt him.

538
00:36:40,708 --> 00:36:44,208
你别以为我们很有钱，只是表面风光
We are not as loaded as it may seem.

539
00:36:44,208 --> 00:36:46,500
卓先生，你怎么才肯放过我丈夫？
Mr Cheuk, can you let my husband go?

540
00:36:46,500 --> 00:36:49,125
要不你开个价，我自己掏腰包⋯
Name a price. I'll pay you from my own pocket…

541
00:36:56,875 --> 00:36:58,042
喂？
Hello?

542
00:36:58,042 --> 00:37:01,208
要不这样，我有八千万现金
I have $80M in cash.

543
00:37:01,208 --> 00:37:02,500
全给你好吗？
Is it OK?

544
00:37:02,792 --> 00:37:04,250
就八千吧
$80M it is!

545
00:37:04,250 --> 00:37:06,208
给我找叶国欢、季正雄！
Find Yip and Kwai!

546
00:37:09,583 --> 00:37:10,375
搞什么？
What the hell?

547
00:37:10,375 --> 00:37:11,958
三大贼王破天荒第一次合作
The 3 Kings of Thieves join forces for the first time.

548
00:37:11,958 --> 00:37:14,083
搞什么都厉害！
It will be terrific no matter what we do!

549
00:37:14,375 --> 00:37:15,500
什么也没想到
You don't even have a plan yet,

550
00:37:15,500 --> 00:37:17,083
找两个通缉犯放在身边
and you want 2 wanted men around you?

551
00:37:17,083 --> 00:37:17,833
我一定能想到
You know I will

552
00:37:17,833 --> 00:37:19,167
你知道我一定能想得到的！
come up with a plan!

553
00:37:19,667 --> 00:37:21,875
这座山，就是我要找的山
This is the mountain I'm looking for.

554
00:37:21,875 --> 00:37:23,958
喜玛拉雅山！
Himalaya!

555
00:37:52,583 --> 00:37:54,083
吃宵夜？
Having night snack?

556
00:37:54,375 --> 00:37:55,333
冰箱有可乐
There's Coke in the fridge.

557
00:37:55,333 --> 00:37:57,042
行，自己来
OK, I'll get it myself.

558
00:38:10,292 --> 00:38:13,833
辉，你朋友要住到什么时候？
Fai, how long is your friend staying?

559
00:38:16,333 --> 00:38:18,125
三、四晚吧
3 or 4 nights.

560
00:38:18,458 --> 00:38:19,917
我们有个女儿
We have a daughter.

561
00:38:19,917 --> 00:38:21,792
突然家中多了个男人
I don't feel comfortable…

562
00:38:21,792 --> 00:38:23,750
不是很方便
with a guy suddenly staying with us.

563
00:38:24,708 --> 00:38:28,042
他做什么工作的？
What does he do?

564
00:38:29,625 --> 00:38:32,833
卖手提电话的
He sells mobile phones.

565
00:38:32,833 --> 00:38:34,250
别说了
Don't worry.

566
00:38:34,750 --> 00:38:36,250
睡吧
Go to sleep.

567
00:38:36,250 --> 00:38:36,792
好的
OK.

568
00:38:36,792 --> 00:38:41,042
我缝好衣服就去睡觉
I'll go to bed after sewing.

569
00:38:47,208 --> 00:38:50,083
正在带客人过来，三分钟到
I will arrive with clients in 3 minutes.

570
00:38:50,250 --> 00:38:51,583
收到
Got it.

571
00:38:55,208 --> 00:38:58,958
阿贵、阿广，卸货，赶快！
Gui, Guang, unload the goods. Be quick.

572
00:39:17,292 --> 00:39:18,500
老大，出事了！
Big Bro, we have a situation!

573
00:39:18,500 --> 00:39:20,333
番禺海关
Panyu Customs!

574
00:39:21,708 --> 00:39:23,708
金，金！
Kam! Kam!

575
00:39:23,708 --> 00:39:25,208
阿忠，停车
Chung, pull over!

576
00:39:29,667 --> 00:39:31,542
你去那边看看
Take a look over there.

577
00:39:31,542 --> 00:39:32,917
你再到那边看一下
Take a look again over there.

578
00:39:34,625 --> 00:39:36,125
别动，手放头上
Don't move. Hands on your head.

579
00:39:36,750 --> 00:39:38,167
走
Let's go.

580
00:39:40,250 --> 00:39:41,583
走啊！
Let's go.

