1169
01:31:34,875 --> 01:31:38,042
陈先生！来，麻烦这边请
Mr Chen. Please follow me.

1170
01:31:38,458 --> 01:31:39,750
请跟我来
This way, please.

1171
01:31:39,750 --> 01:31:40,792
喂
Hey.

1172
01:31:40,792 --> 01:31:41,583
饭到了没？
Where is our rice?

1173
01:31:41,583 --> 01:31:42,917
饭，稍等我一下
Rice? Give me a second.

1174
01:31:42,917 --> 01:31:44,750
饭马上来，很快
Your rice is coming right away.

1175
01:31:47,250 --> 01:31:49,167
不好意思，让你们久等
Sorry to keep you waiting.

1176
01:31:49,167 --> 01:31:50,375
谢谢
Thank you.

1177
01:31:50,375 --> 01:31:51,833
请慢用
Enjoy your food.

1178
01:31:52,333 --> 01:31:54,042
陈先生，这边请
Mr Chen. This way, please.

1179
01:31:54,667 --> 01:31:57,208
喂！你刚不是去厕所吗？
Hey! Haven't you gone to the bathroom just now?

1180
01:31:57,208 --> 01:32:01,000
等等，不要吐，吐在这里
Wait! Don't puke!

1181
01:32:01,542 --> 01:32:03,833
来⋯没事吧？
Are you all right?

1182
01:32:03,833 --> 01:32:06,875
不是去了洗手间吗？怎么会在这里出现
I thought you went to the restroom. Why are you here?

1183
01:32:07,417 --> 01:32:08,750
不好意思，这边请
I'm sorry. This way, please.

1184
01:32:08,750 --> 01:32:10,083
今天真的比较忙一点
We are super busy today.

1185
01:32:10,083 --> 01:32:11,292
喂　　这边请
- Hey!    - This way, please.

1186
01:32:11,292 --> 01:32:12,792
饭是冷的！
The rice is cold!

1187
01:32:13,083 --> 01:32:14,125
稍等我一下
Give me a second.

1188
01:32:14,125 --> 01:32:15,792
不好意思，饭是冷的吗？　　我要茶！
- I'm sorry. The rice is cold?    - I want tea.

1189
01:32:15,792 --> 01:32:17,000
好，等我一下，我帮你换过
Give me a second. I'll give you another bowl.

1190
01:32:17,000 --> 01:32:18,458
快！　　小姐，你告诉我，我自己去找吧
- Quick!    - Tell me the room number. I'll look for it myself.

1191
01:32:18,458 --> 01:32:20,708
我要茶！　　我带你去，等我一下
- I want tea.    - Give me a second.

1192
01:32:20,708 --> 01:32:21,542
茶，我帮你拿
Sure I'll get you tea.

1193
01:32:21,542 --> 01:32:24,333
等一下，你们都等我一下，马上回来
Give me a second. I'll be right back.

1194
01:32:29,375 --> 01:32:31,625
我们不会忘记你们
We should not forget you.

1195
01:32:31,625 --> 01:32:35,125
我们会以最关切的目光
And we should watch with the closest interest

1196
01:32:35,125 --> 01:32:40,917
看着你们开展非凡的新时代
as you embark on this new era of your remarkable history.

